Quentin was pulled over for a traffic violation on Sunday. Racial profiling. Then police illegally started saying they thought he had “something” in this car. HE HAD NOTHING. When he told them that he didn’t, this began. ⁣

They fractured bones in his face, all around his eyes, and damaged ligaments and tendons all over his body. ⁣
⁣
Family and friends reached out to me yesterday to see if I could help. After police did ALL OF THIS, they later admitted that Quentin had nothing suspicious in the car. ⁣
⁣
GIVE ME NAMES AND BADGE NUMBERS PLEASE. ⁣
⁣

While the world only has to deal with the CORONAVIRUS. Black people still have to deal with #Racism and #PoliceBrutality. Smh The attack on our people never stops. 
#POPULATIONCONTROL
